module:
development.folder="dvlp">
module, intelligent schematic, symbol library
This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module to record:
a schematic drawing;
links between the elements of a schematic drawing and the things that they stand for;
a symbol library;
definition of a drawing revision or a drawing sheet revision as a class of document.
the definition of a schematic drawing, including the definition of the elements of the drawing, their composition and connectivity;
the definition of a library of symbols;
the association between an element of a schematic drawing and the thing that is symbolized;
the definition of a class of document that is a drawing revision or a drawing sheet revision.
the nature of the objects that are presented on a schematic drawing. The functional nature of the objects that are presented on a schematic drawing is specified by the Functional_data application module.
The Schematic_document UoF specifies:
the handling of a drawing_revision as a class_of_document; and
the handling of a drawing_sheet_revision as a class_of_document.
drawing_revision_class_of_document 1203
drawing_sheet_revision_class_of_document 1203
